oai_dc:dc.dc:title: [Knoxville Indians] baseball team, ca. 1897
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Composite photograph of [Knoxville Indians] baseball team, ca. 1897. Original is faded sepia with torn and fragile edges. 1 pc. 17 x 13.” This scan is an edited version to enhance the images. Names of players read as: Holland, McClung, Kirby?, Spense, McAttley?, Suttle, S. Spense, Weakley, P. McClung?, [Algernon] Crawley.
